Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_MARCO>
Traders come to this town, right? They don't
come to my town, so I came out here.

<NAME_MOB_MARCO>
Oh, hi. I found a lot of good things to buy here.
Totally worth the trip.

<NAME_MOB_MARCO>
This town must be popular. People back home
keep talking about it.

<NAME_MOB_MARCO>
It's great to have all these traders from all over
the world in one spot like this.

<NAME_MOB_MARCO>
Shoot, if I'd waited one more day, I could have
sold my stuff for so much more...

<NAME_MOB_MARCO>
I'm just not patient enough for this trading
business. I always want to sell my stuff right
away.
